Package com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest.filesystem

The com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest.filesystem package provides interfaces for dealing with the filesystem of the guest operating system.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Directories
    The Directories interface provides methods to manage directories in the guest filesystem.
    DirectoriesTypes
    Defines the data types of the Directories API service.
    Files
    The Files interface provides methods to manage the files in the guest filesystem.
    FilesTypes
    Defines the data types of the Files API service.
    Transfers
    The Transfers interface provides methods to copy files into and out of the guest file system.
    TransfersTypes
    Defines the data types of the Transfers API service.
